      • init

        public ReturnValue init()
        Plugin initialization code goes here. This is the first phase of the plugin lifecycle run. Might do things here like set up database access, create temp files, define defaults, etc. Preprocessing can be done here, although normally processing should be done by/during do_run(). The SEQWARE_SETTINGS file contents is passed in here.
